episodes.title: What is The Bridge to Total Freedom?
episodes.description:
Can I explain the Bridge? I can certainly try! 
Sometimes I forget what words are known or unknow to never-ins. I used OT with no explanation It is short for Operating Thetan. Thetan is kinda the scientology version of the soul and so OT is a soul operating at full potential.

the wiki to the bridge article: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Bridge_to_Total_Freedom
